[B][U]Description[/U][/B] - This tutorial teaches how to create a fun PK area, and the use of a specific operator. (!)

[B][U]Difficulty[/U][/B] - This is [B]very[/B] easy, so I'd say 1/10.

[B][U]Tested Source[/U][/B] - I tested this on Delta, but it should work on any source.

[B][U]Files Modified[/U][/B] - Client class (Client.Java)

